GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 29th November, 2006
8 Agrahayana, 1928 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 29th
November 2006 :-
i)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Coal; and
Shri Shibu Soren relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of Coal.
ii)
(K.L. Sharma)
